{"tid":689331,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"成龍預測巴塞隆拿或 AC米蘭會奪得今屆世界盃","createTime":"2018-06-04T03:51:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T13:13:02.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebb5fe943ffe59ee9c483229fd5956e71130722","tid":689331,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20100713/large/13ec4p14n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100713%2Flarge%2F13ec4p14n.jpg&h=1327410c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成龍上月在美國宣傳電影《功夫夢》（ Karate Kid）時，高呼巴塞隆拿或 AC米蘭會奪得今屆世界盃，此話一出，成龍再次成為網民恥笑對象，連房祖名都要為父親解畫。不過今屆世盃盟主西班牙陣中主力有七位巴塞球員，且完全採用了巴塞的踢法及進攻模式，換句話說，說巴塞捧盃也實不為過。"},{"pid":"524fccadc2f0039951aa61a232b22e0f45a34178","tid":689331,"uid":90422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0b4172b4488b4777a57d08f9aa06cda59a26a4","tid":689331,"uid":36700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:58:14.000Z","msg":"好老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b322668684492b6f048007c53d311770018cdc5e","tid":689331,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"曼聯又贏"},{"pid":"9fa2eb98cdefdbe068953f87a44743c1c5b1ee94","tid":689331,"uid":45487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:05:40.000Z","msg":"巴塞真係憑小白入波贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fecd2c92fdedaae991f945481ff0024c6f0ca7","tid":689331,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"今屆世盃盟主西班牙陣中主力有七位巴塞球員，且完全採用了巴塞的踢法及進攻模式，換句話說，說巴塞捧盃也實不為過。   <br />\n<br />\n結果中左"},{"pid":"d3f18